column5: You have to watch this one it is short,  I think I watched it 100 times in a row. Looks like a Tiger musky, but it's a pike somewhere in Europe. Someone mentioned to me that one of the fish swimming around is found in europe, I thought tiger at first.
Definately gonna need a little Pepto-Bismol.
HAHA! That's hilarious!  .....hey  shouldn't you be working?
Hence, the need for large baits.  :-)
Wonder what the aftermath of THAT was..... I once found a 4lb Walleye with a 3lb walleye in its throat..both dead!!!
